-- Merkel Says She Backs 1% of Euro-Area GDP for Growth Pact
-- B y   L e o n   M a n g a s a r i a n
-- 2012-06-22T14:16:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-22/merkel-says-she-backs-1-of-euro-area-gdp-for-growth-pact.html
German  Chancellor Angela Merkel  said
she backed calls by European leaders for a growth pact of 1
percent of the euro area’s gross domestic product. This would be
a “good sign,” Merkel told reporters at a news conference
today in Rome with French President Francois Hollande, Spanish
Prime Minister Mariano Rajoy and Italian Prime Minister Mario
Monti.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Leon Mangasarian at 
 lmangasarian@bloomberg.net  